<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{alertTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%), linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .header.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
        }
        
        .header.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
        }
        
        .header.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        }
        
        .header.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .alert-card {
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .alert-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            transform: translate(30px, -30px);
        }
        
        .alert-card.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
            border-left-color: #ef4444;
        }
        
        .alert-card.error::before {
            background: #ef4444;
        }
        
        .alert-card.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fefbf3 0%, #fef3c7 100%);
            border-left-color: #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .alert-card.warning::before {
            background: #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .alert-card.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
            border-left-color: #10b981;
        }
        
        .alert-card.success::before {
            background: #10b981;
        }
        
        .alert-card.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
            border-left-color: #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .alert-card.info::before {
            background: #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .alert-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .alert-title.error {
            color: #b91c1c;
        }
        
        .alert-title.warning {
            color: #92400e;
        }
        
        .alert-title.success {
            color: #065f46;
        }
        
        .alert-title.info {
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .alert-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .alert-message.error {
            color: #7f1d1d;
        }
        
        .alert-message.warning {
            color: #78350f;
        }
        
        .alert-message.success {
            color: #064e3b;
        }
        
        .alert-message.info {
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .timestamp {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .alert-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .alert-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .alert-icon {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{alertType}}">
            <h1>System Alert</h1>
            <p>{{alertTitle}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            {{#if recipientName}}
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{recipientName}},
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="alert-card {{alertType}}">
                <div class="alert-icon">
                    {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}üö®{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'warning'}}‚ö†Ô∏è{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'success'}}‚úÖ{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'info'}}‚ÑπÔ∏è{{/if}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="alert-title {{alertType}}">
                    {{alertTitle}}
                </div>
                
                <div class="alert-message {{alertType}}">
                    {{alertMessage}}
                </div>
                
                {{#if actionUrl}}
                <div class="cta-section">
                    <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button {{alertType}}">
                        {{#if actionText}}{{actionText}}{{else}}Learn More{{/if}}
                    </a>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="timestamp">
                <strong>Time:</strong> {{formatDate timestamp 'long'}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}
                We know how frustrating technical issues can be, especially when you're in the flow of learning. Our entire team is focused on resolving this quickly so you can get back to what matters most - your progress. We truly appreciate your patience and are here to support you through this.
                {{else if eq alertType 'warning'}}
                We're sharing this important update because we respect your time and want you to plan accordingly. Transparency is important to us, and we believe you deserve to know what's happening with your learning platform. As always, we're here if you have any questions.
                {{else if eq alertType 'success'}}
                Great news to share! üéâ We love celebrating positive updates with our learning community. Thank you for being part of what makes {{companyName}} special - your engagement and feedback help us continuously improve.
                {{else}}
                We believe in keeping you informed about your learning platform. This update helps ensure you have the latest information to make the most of your {{companyName}} experience. Knowledge is power, especially when it comes to your own learning journey!
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}
            <div class="message">
                <strong>What you can do:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Check our status page for real-time updates</li>
                    <li>Try refreshing the page or logging out and back in</li>
                    <li>Contact support if the issue persists</li>
                    <li>Follow our social media for the latest updates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>{{companyName}} System Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 